data.description: If you are looking for privacy and Beautiful Views than this 3 Bedroom ranch home is it!  This cozy home features many updates....3 bedrooms, eat in kitchen and laundry, spacious updated ceramic bath with walk in shower.  There is a detached 1 car garage just outside the mud room off of the kitchen.  The outside offers 17+ gorgeous acres with Spectacular Views!, lots of area to relax, play, build on and enjoy but close enough to shopping, schools and major highways.
